<noinclude>
This is the "Metaphor" template.  While the name is Metaphor, it is used to display members of the VettedMetaphor category.
It should be called in the following format:
<pre>
{{Metaphor
|Name gloss=
|Name transcription=
|Aliases={{Metaphor.Alias}}
|Description=
|Comments=
|Family=
|Tags=
|Metaphor Level=
|Metaphor Type=
|Experiential basis=
|Investigated for=
|Source frame=
|Target frame=
|Mappings={{Mapping}}
|Related metaphors={{Related metaphor}}
|Entailments={{Entailment}}
|Examples={{Example}}
|Entered by=
|Last reviewed by=
|Status=
|Program alias=
|LinkEnglish=
|LinkSpanish=
|LinkPersian=
|LinkRussian=
}}
</pre>
Edit the page to see the template text.
</noinclude><includeonly>{| class="wikitable"
