'''Examples from linked Linguistic metaphors:'''
{{#ask:[[Is example of.Is instance of CM::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]]
|mainlabel=-
|?Is example of=Example.LM
|?Has text=Example.Text
|?Has provenance=Example.Provenance
|?Is from language=Example.Language
|?Has comments=Example.Comments
|?Has text gloss=Example.Gloss
|?Has English translation=Example.English translation
|?Has annotation=Example.Annotation
|format=template
|template=ExamplesOfLM
|named args=yes
}}{{#ask:[[Is example of.Was found using seed.Is instance of CM::{{FULLPAGENAME}}]]
|mainlabel=-
|?Is example of=Example.LM
|?Has text=Example.Text
|?Has provenance=Example.Provenance
|?Is from language=Example.Language
|?Has comments=Example.Comments
|?Has text gloss=Example.Gloss
|?Has English translation=Example.English translation
|?Has annotation=Example.Annotation
|format=template
|template=ExamplesOfLM
|named args=yes
}}
